romWeb?topicID=14956.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 1hs damage bonus</span><hr size=1> They didn't add to the 1h weapons, they merely made the existing ones visible.<br><br>On the other hand they did add to the 2h bonus.<br><br>Damage bonuses have always increased with level, if you check the Tomes you can find the 1h bonus formula, unfortunately I don't think anyone has done a 2h formula with the new additions. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6318"><img src="http://www3.sympatico.ca/lchisholm/luth_sig.jpg" border=0></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubeldukil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Beldukil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 3667<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/20/02 7:26:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14956.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://beld.freeservers.com/images/beld.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 1hs damage bonus</span><hr size=1> There was always a damage bonus on main hand 1h and 2h weapons.<br><br>Before kunark both were 8 at level 50. After kunark both were 11 at level 60.<br><br>2h was then increased to about 22 for all 2h weapons.<br><br>Now 2h scales with delay over level 50.<br><br>At 60 a 40 delay 2h has a 34 damage bonus.<br><br>At 60 a 1h weapon still has only an 11 damage bonus. <p><center><imgsrc="http://beld.freeservers.com/images/beld.jpg"> <br><table border=0>  <tr><td><imgsrc="http://www.wise.k12.va.us/cms/images/animatedKnightLeft.gif">    </td><td>Beldukil Lawbringer<br> Level 60 Crusader of Tunare<br>Innit<br>Xev<br>    </td><td><img src="http://www.wise.k12.va.us/cms/images/animatedKnightLeft.gif"></td></